## Remarkable stuff

Make a backup
```
ssh -t root@reMarkable "tar czvf - /home/root" > "home_root-$(date +'%y%m%d-%H%M%S').tar.gz"
```

```
ssh root@10.11.99.1 rm-ssh-over-wlan on
```

```
Host rm3
	HostName imx8mm-ferrari
	User root
```

```
convert *.* -auto-orient ../pictures.pdf
```


